OL,3,CChancellor's 'Great British Summer
OL,4,CSaving' is more modest than it sounds
OL,6,FThe chancellor told ITV News Economics
OL,7,FEditor Joel Hills that every little
OL,8,Fhelps when it comes to supporting
OL,9,Fhouseholds with the cost of living
OL,10,Fcrisis
OL,12,F"The Great British Summer Saving".
OL,14,FIt's a terrific marketing slogan - the
OL,15,Fgovernment has even rustled up a logo.
OL,16,FBut will it live up to the hype?
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@aO]
