OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779451869
OL,3,CChancellor's 'Great British Summer
OL,4,CSaving' is more modest than it sounds
OL,6,FFirst, the scale: #1.8 billion of
OL,7,Ffinancial support for households and
OL,8,Fbusinesses is tiny compared with the
OL,9,F#78 billion made available in the two
OL,10,Fyears after Russia invaded Ukraine.
OL,12,FThe squeeze on living standards this
OL,13,Ftime looks smaller too. As the
OL,14,Fchancellor says, "every little helps",
OL,15,Fbut there is a limit to how much this
OL,16,Fwill be felt.
OL,26,@vD@ROUvD@eO]
