CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779451869
OL,3,CChancellor's 'Great British Summer
OL,4,CSaving' is more modest than it sounds
OL,6,FWhen it comes to households, the bulk
OL,7,Fof the "savings" on offer are being
OL,8,Ftargeted at anyone with a car, and
OL,9,Ffamilies heading out with the kids
OL,10,Fduring the summer holidays.
OL,12,FFair enough. But not everyone can
OL,13,Fafford to go to theme parks or run a
OL,14,Fcar. There isn't much on offer here
OL,15,Ffor those on the lowest incomes.
OL,17,FWhat's really interesting is what the
OL,18,Fchancellor hasn't done.
OL,26,@oD@HOUoD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
