OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779451869
OL,3,CChancellor's 'Great British Summer
OL,4,CSaving' is more modest than it sounds
OL,6,FThe risk here is that if the war drags
OL,7,Fon and if the market price of oil and
OL,8,Fgas remains elevated, the squeeze on
OL,9,Fliving standards will tighten as we
OL,10,Fhead into winter and the central
OL,11,Fheating gets switched on again.
OL,13,FReeves acknowledged today that she may
OL,14,Fneed to take further action in
OL,15,FSeptember. If she is still chancellor,
OL,16,Fof course.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
